    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a parts car. The engine currently runs roughly and will likely require a major overhaul, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, there is significant rust on the rocker panels and several large dents along the passenger side. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It is recommended that the buyer hauls the vehicle away as it is not currently reliable for long-distance driving.",
      "price": 4000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
